---
title: Hoisin Pork & Mushroom Rice Bowl with Sesame Aioli
description: This dish is an irresistible combination of baby spinach, tasty pork and garlicky rice, with the feel-good factor of cooking a
wholesome meal from scratch. The best part is the sesame aioli to make it super satisfying.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/hoisin-pork-mushroom-rice-bowl-8bc188a4.jpg
